articles.title: Niger coup leaders dissolve govt, declare Tiani head of state - Reuters
articles.description: Leaders of a coup in Niger declared General Abdourahamane Tiani as the new head of state on Friday days after saying they had ousted President Mohamed Bazoum in the seventh military takeover in West and Central Africa in less than three years.
